videoSnippet.title: Mikhail Tal the Great, Mates in Eight! (12 years old)
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator 12 year old Mikhail Tal blunders a piece but then finds a forced checkmate in 8 moves!

Can you find it as well? :)

Mikhail Tal vs Josif Israel Zilber
Riga (1949) 
1. e4 e6 2. d4 d5 3. Nd2 c5 4. ed5 Qd5 5. Ngf3 Nc6 6. Bc4 Qh5 7. dc5 Bc5 8. Ne4 Nge7 9. Bg5 Qg4 10. Qd3 b6 11. O-O-O O-O 12. Bf6 Qf4 13. Kb1 gf6 14. g3 Qh6 15. g4 Qf4 16. g5 fg5 17. Nfg5 Ng6 18. h4 Nb4 19. Qh3 e5 20. Qg2 Bf5 21. h5 Kg7 22. hg6 h6 23. Bf7 Rf7 24. gf7 hg5 25. Ng5 Qf2 26. Ne6 Kf7 27. Qg7 Ke6 28. Rh6 Bg6 29. Qg6 Ke7 30. Rh7 Kf8 31. Qg7 Ke8 32. Qd7 Kf8 33. Rh8#
